{
  "stem": "162.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they requested workers from the camp where my mother was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they requested my mother to be among them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't ask me how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe they told them that they heard this woman was a good worker, or that she's got relatives here in this-- in-- in my place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my mother ended up coming to be with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'll never forget it because in those days, you had to walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she walked from the train station in Belzec out to this estate, which was another maybe 10, five miles or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went to meet her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'll never forget this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I saw this-- see this woman coming in the distance towards me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it's my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's how I got reunited with my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we're all at this estate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the war, every day, we would watch the planes go into Berlin to do their bombing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this was like a constant humming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You never forget that humming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were like 20, 30 planes at a time that would fly across-- Russian?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they must have been Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russians, Americans, English, British, I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were coming to bomb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a terrible time because, you know, even though we were safe there, we never knew how long we were going to be safe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, somebody in the village-- this estate was in a small village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody came through the village and said that the Russians are coming close.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians are coming tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whoever wants to leave, if they're-- if they're afraid, they can leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
